{"tid":2329440,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【中國封殺澳洲煤炭後  開始限電】","createTime":"2020-12-17T08:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T17:57:03.000Z","uid":134993,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"fc6803c25df6f4c58bc895e439cf93e474ab184d","tid":2329440,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:40:40.000Z","msg":"制裁澳洲的代價，會不會太大了⋯<br />\n<br />\n// 對於煤炭儲量豐富、產量創紀錄的中國而言，煤炭價格實屬高位。然而Wood Mackenzie的一份報告稱，此時此刻出現的短缺令動力煤市場陷入「混亂」。報告稱，隨著取暖需求激增，一些省份出現了拉閘限電現象。上周，動力煤期貨價格創下歷史新高，但現在正在響應政府在關鍵的冬季為市場降溫的努力⋯<br />\n<br />\n而據《自由亞洲電台》，浙江、湖南等地為節省用煤，發改委下令晚間交通燈及路燈關閉 //<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3r76eA3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3r76eA3&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28cdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=f5006bbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3r76eA3</a><br />\n<br />\n相關報道：<br />\n地方政府為節省用煤發布限電令<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/37qJbs0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37qJbs0&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28cdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=8923907f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/37qJbs0</a>"},{"pid":"5d992e12ce9ae819d56212b31bfb35fc2aa14050","tid":2329440,"uid":14103,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"CCTVB冇講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba260e095548c6b63132201edfbe29ff89bfbaf7","tid":2329440,"uid":282930,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"石頭⋯⋯腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb72e9d66be2d640f817e9a09fbac9aaf4b18a2","tid":2329440,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:46:29.000Z","msg":"搬石頭砸自己的腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/h